data.oai_dc:dc: FPLC absorbance time-series output for the second (after completion of treatments, t=1) venom extraction. Each of the four treatments are presented on separate sheets. Each column is a different scorpion, values are absorbance at 280nm. The leftmost column specifies the volume eluted in mL (beginning at 5mL due to an initial 5 mL to prime the equipment).
